c: 43
v: 32
t: "Bangabahlula-hluli benceba yeNkosi yakho na? Sithi nje Ababakhethele indlela yokuphila kubomi beli hlabathi, Saphakamisa abanye babo bangentla kwabanye ngokwamabakala khona ukuze bakwazi ukusebenzisana ngokwengqesho. Kodwa inceba yeNkosi yakho yiyona ingcono ngaphezu kwako konke abakuwanqayo"